title: Wonderland
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Turkish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Customers are mostly Bogazici students and prices are inexpensive to moderate. You could ask staff to prepare the vegetarian dishes as vegan (omitting cheese, egg, etc.). Around 20% of the menu is vegetarian and are marked with "V," which is uncommon assistance for Turkish restaurants.
